--- !u!114 &1225791647
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1225791645}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f88e07aba5f299b43ac2e86d54427d17, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialManager
  sentences:
  - Hey! Welcome to the adventure. Move using WASD or the Arrow Keys.
  - See those platforms? Use Q and E to switch between colors and see if you can
    find your way to the other side.
  - Nice! Watch out for enemies. They can attack you at anytime, but you can only
    defeat them in Green mode by clicking.
  - Good job! Check out those portals, which you can enter through the Blue mode.
  - You'll see a tall wall, built with reinforced bricks. They can only be disabled
    by a button found in Red mode.
  - You might notice a portal is located on top of a Green platform. Use Shift+Q
    or Shift+E to use multiple colors at once! Careful, the effect only lasts 2 seconds
    and has a cooldown of 4 seconds.
  - Incredible work! Use your skills to get to the end.
  tutorialOverlay: {fileID: 747951675}
  tutorialText: {fileID: 2028226750}
